{"tid":1083600,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"痴線～Marvel 究然同出名侵權嘅 Miniso名創優品 合作","createTime":"2019-03-29T17:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T05:41:37.000Z","uid":169648,"like":26,"dislike":332,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"43a07b6ec50ca02f77492d9c0d72f3eab1ef403c","tid":1083600,"uid":169648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photos.prnasia.com/prnk/20190322/2411390-1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotos.prnasia.com%2Fprnk%2F20190322%2F2411390-1&h=b76c0248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n零售品牌名創優品正式宣佈與全球頂級 IP 漫威開展官方合作，開發一系列周邊產品，並面向一百多個國家進行銷售。<br />\n<br />\n發佈會現場設置了 MINISO x MARVEL 產品展示區域，展示漫威 IP 產品多達2000個，涵蓋了蜘蛛俠、美國隊長、Iron Man、Hulk、Marvel隊長、雷神、黑寡婦等深入人心的英雄形象。<br />\n這也是名創優品繼 2018 年牽手 Hello Kitty、探險活寶 Adventure Time、We Bare Bears、粉紅豹、Pantone、芝麻街等知名 IP 之後，與漫威開展深度合作的原因，「名創優品會一如既往地遵循優質低價的產品理念，為世界各地的漫威迷帶去一流品質、親民價格的正版周邊產品。」<br />\n<br />\n此次名創優品與漫威合作推出的周邊產品，除了在產品設計、質量方面做到極致外，價格也非常具有市場競爭力。譬如一款精美的馬克杯，售價最低只要7.9元人民幣，一款漫威英雄形象的小擺件售價僅10元人民幣，而一般精品商店同類產品的起價是100元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n在名創優品看來，高性價比的產品永遠是打開全球市場的利器，因為秉持了這一理念，使得名創優品能夠在5年多的時間內，迅速進入到80多個國家的零售市場。截至目前，名創優品全球門店數已超過3500家，在2018年，創下了超過170億人民幣的銷售收入。<br />\n<br />\n名創優品通過不斷與世界知名 IP 合作，一方面借助 IP 的號召力，促進了產品銷售，另一方面借助 IP 的影響力，提升了品牌知名度和美譽度，在生活家居市場探索出了一套獨有的「名創優品模式」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.prnasia.com/story/240630-2.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.prnasia.com%2Fstory%2F240630-2.shtml&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7T%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=61b9d420\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.prnasia.com/story/240630-2.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"72c975cb523720253f2b11cb2210802755bd7c9e","tid":1083600,"uid":169648,"like":285,"dislike":1,"score":284,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:29:40.000Z","msg":"名創優品唔單止 LOGO 抄 UNIQLO，連UNIQLO 玩 Crossover Tee 條水都抄足"},{"pid":"f18687ac563a1b7266248274af0f93cfcdd5562a","tid":1083600,"uid":64374,"like":428,"dislike":33,"score":395,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:36:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f1ca5e7972ca04ac5851adf61c655752165fff8","tid":1083600,"uid":38472,"like":99,"dislike":1,"score":98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:37:39.000Z","msg":"果然無恥先成功。"},{"pid":"593b87e5bfd652569ccbc7e11d330bf6f358e4a3","tid":1083600,"uid":71133,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:37:55.000Z","msg":"fake it till you make it"},{"pid":"97dcf09f0150b0b41eeff1d89865a679bef012a8","tid":1083600,"uid":169648,"like":95,"dislike":2,"score":93,"quote":{"pid":"72c975cb523720253f2b11cb2210802755bd7c9e","tid":1083600,"uid":169648,"like":285,"dislike":1,"score":284,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:29:40.000Z","msg":"名創優品唔單止 LOGO 抄 UNIQLO，連UNIQLO 玩 Crossover Tee 條水都抄足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:41:57.000Z","msg":"你抄人，人抄你。<br />\n玩爛晒件事為止<br />\n<img src=\"https://w7n4r7h4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/UNIQLO-logo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fw7n4r7h4.stackpathcdn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2FUNIQLO-logo.png&h=b14decbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/119096/org/fe6ae612d7671b9bfe637911e8012cc4.jpg/vLCqc3MEzjdJQXFPsweeiwsKGCd5339Mx0i_3cdIv90?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F119096%2Forg%2Ffe6ae612d7671b9bfe637911e8012cc4.jpg%2FvLCqc3MEzjdJQXFPsweeiwsKGCd5339Mx0i_3cdIv90%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=818279dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f8bb920edc1346702c109a2b9f3768a92c01e19","tid":1083600,"uid":84926,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:42:16.000Z","msg":"乜撚野世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b68133510b2f4e253f8e1c88e36bc0debe9c300","tid":1083600,"uid":169648,"like":171,"dislike":3,"score":168,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T18:02:23.000Z","msg":"屌你！幾時俾返錢兩位香港插畫師！<br />\n<br />\n仲記得 2016 年 名創優品開店時，抄襲香港漫畫家江記的漫畫角色「企鵝丁丁」做產品，之後又抄襲香港插畫師 Daryl Cheung 設計的卡通小熊「白白」，用作智能電話殼的圖案。<br />\n<br />\n名創優品的黃樹豐接受傳媒訪問時強調不介意「抄襲」和「山寨」等指控，認為「起碼有noise」，又強調一直尊重知識產權。<br />\n<br />\n原作「企鵝丁丁」<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.academy.arts-news.net/sites/default/files/Artsnap%E6%B1%9F%E8%A8%986.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.academy.arts-news.net%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FArtsnap%25E6%25B1%259F%25E8%25A8%25986.jpg&h=dc24b83c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n名創優品涉侵權產品<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/118847/org/a00346a6853560145b85957e0f69c6f2.jpg/ToJwM0f62I8-Mtm7t928d8eV3tWITdVkHjzXGR481xk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F118847%2Forg%2Fa00346a6853560145b85957e0f69c6f2.jpg%2FToJwM0f62I8-Mtm7t928d8eV3tWITdVkHjzXGR481xk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c8027729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原作「白白熊」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2015-02-16/900/20150216002026.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2015-02-16%2F900%2F20150216002026.jpg&h=16099d6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n名創優品涉侵權產品<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/118890/org/cf3f76e24336a2ba6b3f779bfa8fb68f.jpg/3kc2R4fPMv4RuBQrP45swG9fnRrtQZlVmexagpnsWoI?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F118890%2Forg%2Fcf3f76e24336a2ba6b3f779bfa8fb68f.jpg%2F3kc2R4fPMv4RuBQrP45swG9fnRrtQZlVmexagpnsWoI%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=6f6d3020&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce4999aa27319e918e4235ec6f2ae346e969b0a9","tid":1083600,"uid":28195,"like":156,"dislike":1,"score":155,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T18:19:30.000Z","msg":"好明顯，Miniso背後勢力並不簡單。"},{"pid":"c5a14a589f6d2c5f17aae73a2c7bac4f5ef622d5","tid":1083600,"uid":169648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T19:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4920ca7025e83bec855c682274b63c01431868f9","tid":1083600,"uid":40199,"like":1